 bị thích khách tấn công...</p>","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"48492","season":null,"vote_average":6.539,"vote_count":423},"modified":"2023-03-17T21:40:58.000Z","cast":["Lưu Đức Hoa","Lý Băng Băng","Đặng Siêu","Lương Gia Huy","Lưu Gia Linh","Ngô Diệu Hán","Teddy Robin","Liu Jinshan","Yao Lu","Vương Đức Thuận","Hà Thịnh Minh","Huang Yonggang","Trần Hiểu","Jean-Michel Casanova","Sos Haroyan"],"director":["Tsui Hark","Hark Tsui"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Lưu Đức Hoa","name_vi":"Lưu Đức Hoa","name_original":"Andy Lau","tmdb_id":25246,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/z9R2yerjfgxwDWIH8sjiS0hhcre.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/25246"},{"name":"Lý Băng Băng","name_vi":"Lý Băng Băng","name_original":"Li Bingbing","tmdb_id":109432,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gBDRToPG0smAFSUpWT5pmJv2fJr.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/109432"},{"name":"Đặng Siêu","name_vi":"Đặng Siêu","name_original":"Deng Chao","tmdb_id":99689,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k2pylMn5jG6z3KGrQOXP473ULNK.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/99689"},{"name":"Lương Gia Huy","name_vi":"Lương Gia Huy","name_original":"Tony Leung Ka-fai","tmdb_id":56861,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/il4L0QSp5STfZCB1wsvb6rSCDar.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/56861"},{"name":"Lưu Gia Linh","name_vi":"Lưu Gia Linh","name_original":"Carina Lau","tmdb_id":12672,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5Va4jk69gkdAcABtkTtcUz85RLA.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/12672"},{"name":"Ngô Diệu Hán","name_vi":"Ngô Diệu Hán","name_original":"Richard Ng Yiu-Hon","tmdb_id":62417,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8ZyqXi66gyxeR5crT51TJ6YTMWM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/62417"},{"name":"Teddy Robin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Teddy Robin","tmdb_id":26729,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/H0m6swp53hydoCTUHivklF3US0.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/